{"tid":289481,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"同樊少皇結婚兩年 36歲賈曉晨成功陀B","createTime":"2017-06-19T04:47:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T13:37:48.000Z","uid":42804,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2c94c4ff676aec27c1f0d90951b81d4f077411e9","tid":289481,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T04:47:43.000Z","msg":"現年45歲「力王」樊少皇同36歲女友賈曉晨（JJ），拍拖以嚟，外界一直唔睇好戀情，結果二人排除萬難喺15年結婚。<br />\n<br />\n婚後二人雖然喺大陸搏命搵錢，但一直努力造人嘅佢哋，終於成功陀B。今日凌晨JJ就喺微博貼咗一張着住白色短裙嘅相。相中見佢個肚已經籮咁大，而JJ更不其然將隻手揞住腹部，目測起碼有5個月身孕。JJ留言祝今日生日嘅老公話：「蛋皇@樊少皇，全家祝你生日快乐！永远幸福！」相中除咗有兩公婆所養嘅三隻愛犬，唔知JJ所講嘅「全家」，係咪仲包括埋肚裡面個BB呢？<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56847581&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170619\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56847581%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170619&d=zGjnhggtEuWaQdY2yEmPV%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=4c9fe20d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56847581%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170619&h=3cacaeb7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56847581&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170619</a>"},{"pid":"cc3858eb20ad0cbe74cc54171e0d097761b4c1da","tid":289481,"uid":2914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T04:52:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/19/125232_bef2fbf9340984d5132f0014f5b56b5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F19%2F125232_bef2fbf9340984d5132f0014f5b56b5a.jpg&h=7db87552&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"260d6918aa642891359e1d4541c4eceaaac8bb11","tid":289481,"uid":81742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T04:58:11.000Z","msg":"佐佐木<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89